title: Net Percentage of Domestic Banks Tightening Standards for Consumer Loans Excluding Credit Card (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
The FRED series Net Percentage of Domestic Respondents Tightening Standards on Other Consumer Loans is now known as Net Percentage of Domestic Banks Tightening Standards for Consumer Loans Excluding Credit Card.

For further information, please refer to the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System's Senior Loan Officer Opinion Survey on Bank Lending Practices release, online at http://www.federalreserve.gov/boarddocs/SnLoanSurvey/.
